Wouldn’t it be fantastic if you – no matter who you are or where you come from – could put forward your situation and need - and ask for a micro loan to get a business started, help grow a business, or simply provide a loan (that may or may not be repaid) to someone to help them install basic sanitation in their home. 
Matt and Veronika are lucky enough to be in a position to open our own business after Matt was made redundant from an IT company in February 2015. We’ve decided that even before we sell any product, we would like to give others the same opportunity so we have decided to invest 1% of our starting capital into www.kiva.org loans.

Once we become profitable, we plan to invest more money into Kiva which we will continually rotate into new loans as it gets repaid.
